{
  "stem": "26672.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But nevertheless, you-- you-- you managed to survive, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was taken to the camps, and I overheard a group trying to-- to escape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And each one had to find their own firearms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But before that, I was working in coal mine-- not in coal mines, working in coal piles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were unloading-- unloading coal or cement or helping bombs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was an airfield at an Air Force Base.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So therefore, people were needed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One day, a plane came down on fire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And some of the-- don't know exactly how many-- they ran forwards and kicked the-- the cockpit open and saved this pilot, a German pilot, obviously.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was sent for recuperation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when he came back, he came back with some goods for these people who saved him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they were made sort of capos of the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they had freedom to move with more movement than the others.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I overheard one night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were talking about getting a group together to escape, because they had more access to it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One was quite a tall man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't remember his name, but I remember he was a good-looking man-- a very good-looking man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they managed to find some-- break into a warehouse and steal uniforms and guns.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "As a group, about 10 of them did escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I heard that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In those days, although my, whatever job I had-- I also cleaned rooms for German officers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They gave to me extra food, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When I heard that they was trying to escape and you had to have your own weapons with, I managed to-- to find whether he's kept his revolver in his bag, covered.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the holsters, the German holsters, were very heavy leather, so I only took the revolver.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
